'''Random House Audio''' is an imprint of the Penguin Random House Audio Publishing Group, a subsidiary of [[Random House|Penguin Random House]].<ref name="PRHAP" /> It is responsible for publishing many of the audio versions of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' novels, including the digital re-release of the ''Star Wars'' audiobook catalogue from [[Bantam Doubleday Dell Audio Publishing]].

